 ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
                   CVC COVERAGE HELPER PROGRAMS - SOURCE FILES
 ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

 - see the '../README.coverage.helper-programs' on level up for more
   information on these files.

 - these helper programs are pre-compiled in ../bin, but are available if you
   desire to change them:

- edit the makefile.lnx to choose 64 bit, 32 bit and whether you want -g on   
   makefile -f maefile.lnx <nbame of helper program to make>

- there are some extern procs for reading, building the toggle dat netlist
  and other operations in the file tgldat_srvc.c (services) if you want to
  write your own analysis program.
